# Babblers- NIIT Project ②

Software
i	Eclipse Neon
ii	Oracle XE 11g
iii	Tomcat 9.0

Project Structure
SRC/main/Java
    i	com.niit.controllers : All the classes are annotated with @Controller and @RestController so that they can be scanned by spring MVC
        a	Navigation.java :  Contains MVC controller methods for basic navigation.
        b	RC_Blog : Contains RestWebServices related to Blog.
        c	RC_Forum : Contains RestWebServices related to Forum.
        d	RC_ForumComments: Contains RestWebServices related to ForumComments.
        e	RC_BlogRating: Contains RestWebServices related to BlogRating.

    ii	com.niit.models : Contains all model classes.
        a	Blog.java
        b	BlogRating.java
        c	Forum.java
        d	ForumComments.java
        e	User.java
        f	Message.java
        g	OutputMessage.java

iii	com.niit.DAO : Contains all DAO interfaces and DAOImpls containing persistence Logic.
    a	DAO and DAO Implementation.

iv	com.niit.Service: Contains all service Interface and ServiceImpl containing business logic.
    a	ServiceInterface and Service Implementations. 
    
SRC/main/Webapp
i	Resources
    a	CSS : Contains all User Interface framework css and custom css.
        •	Bootstrap.min.css
        •	Bootstrape-theme.css
        •	Font-awesome.min.css
        •	Demo.css
    b	JS : Contains all java script files and angular controllers.
        •	AngularController : Contains all the JavaScript source files related to Angular js.
            (1)	 App.js
            (2)	 Blog.js
            (3)	 Forum.js
            (4)	 ForumComments.js
            (5)	 BlogRating.js
            (6)	 FindFriends.js
            (7)	 IndividualBlog.js
            (8)	 IndividualForum.js
            (9)	 Profile.js
    c	Fonts : Contains all the fonts files.
    d	Images : Contains static image used in UI.

ii	 Web-Inf
    a	Includes
        •	Frameworks.jsp : Contains code for importing all the mandatory imports like css,angular controllers, custom j's files. This file is imported on the home page.
        •	Header.jsp : Contains the header navigation bar.
        •	Footer.jsp : Contains footer code.
        •	Modal registration : Contains code for modal registration.
        •	Modal login : Contains code for modal login.
    b	Views : Contains all the dynamic web pages.
    c	ApplicationContext Config.xml : Contains data source information and hibernate configuration.
    d	Dispatcher-servlet.xml : Contains all spring  MVC configuration.
    e	Spring-security.xml : Contains all configuration related to spring security.
    f	Web.xml : Deployment descriptor.


